</p>

<p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
If you are in the town centre or an older terraced street, check parking and any loading restrictions in advance and let us know, so we can plan the closest safe access for the van. For a full step-by-step plan, our <a href="/move-checklist/" class="text-[#071059] hover:underline font-medium">moving house checklist</a> walks you through the weeks before your move.
</p>

<p class="text-gray-700">
